subtittle: Created responsive dashboard with key metrics
description: Designed and implemented a comprehensive user dashboard that displays important metrics and information. Used React with TypeScript for component development, incorporated data visualization libraries for charts and graphs, and ensured the interface is responsive across all device sizes. Implemented real-time data updates using React Query.

subtittle: Developed interactive chat interface with real-time responses
description: Created a modern, user-friendly chat interface for the prototype chatbot application. Implemented message threading, typing indicators, and response animations. Designed the UI to be accessible and responsive across all device types. Used TypeScript and React for frontend implementation with Go backend integration for processing user queries.

subtittle: Connected frontend with Go-based NLP backend
description: Integrated the frontend chat application with the Go-based Natural Language Processing backend. Implemented a service layer for API communication, set up proper error handling and retry mechanisms, and created a seamless user experience by managing loading states. Enhanced the response display with proper formatting for different content types returned by the NLP engine.

subtittle: Created comprehensive technical documentation and project roadmap
description: Led the documentation effort for the senior capstone project, creating detailed technical specifications, architecture diagrams, and implementation guidelines. Established a clear project roadmap with milestones, deadlines, and team member responsibilities. Set up project management tools and workflows to track progress efficiently.

subtittle: Conducted stakeholder interviews and developed user stories
description: Performed comprehensive requirements gathering through stakeholder interviews and market research. Translated business requirements into detailed user stories with acceptance criteria. Created user journey maps and wireframes to illustrate the proposed solution. Prioritized features based on business value and implementation complexity.
